The method `AddArmClient<TBuilder, TConfiguration>` calls `builder.RegisterClientFactory<ArmClient, ArmClientOptions>(configuration)` which has `[RequiresUnreferencedCode]` and `[RequiresDynamicCode]`. Propagate these attributes to the method:

